text:
Darn. It's weird that <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/hubl/tags/dnd-areas|their documentation> is missing all this stuff...

Even for stuff like padding, nowhere does it list that you can do stuff like they do in their website boilerplate, eg:

```    padding={
      "default": {
        "top": 0,
        "right": 64,
        "bottom": 0,
        "left": 0
      },
      "mobile": {
        "top": 0,
        "right": 0,
        "bottom": 0,
        "left": 0
      }
    }```
The desktop/mobile settings aren't mentioned in the documentation, but it's syntax that's supported...
